title: Issue when using "6) export AMP as dfm"
body:
THIS IS NOT TECH SUPPORT FOR NEWBIE FAKERS
POST ONLY ISSUES RELATED TO BUGS OR CODE

## Expected behavior
When trying to use "6) train AMP SRC-SRC" to use for DeepFaceLive, everything looked fine. No errors.

## Actual behavior

After letting it train for an hour, I wanted to test it and see if it will work. When trying to export it as a .dfm model this error ocurrs.
